    ------------------------------------------
    rrdreport - an RRD reporting tool for MRTG
    by Max Clark <max@clarksys.com>
    ------------------------------------------

rrdreport is composed of several perl scripts that read data from a RRD 
database and generates a report.

Get it from:

	https://github.com/maxclark/rrdreport
	=====================================


Required Modules
----------------

- DBI and DBD::Pg or DBD::MySQL
  -> get it from CPAN

Note that several Linux distributions will already have these modules as RPMs.


